---
title: Indonesian-Inspired Pork with Sticky Coconut Rice
description: Sweet, savoury and peanutty – this recipe contains the tri-fecta of Javanese flavours with just the right amount of spice. Add a squirt of lime juice and you'll be transported!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indonesian-inspired-pork-e15dfe0c.jpg
